headline: Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE:HPE) Powers Skild AI's High-Performance Expansion With NVIDIA Solutions
summary: Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE:HPE) has partnered with Skild AI to provide infrastructure for the development of advanced AI technologies, including the Skild Brain, which aims for real-time data processing and human-like learning capabilities using HPE's storage and NVIDIA-accelerated computing. Despite these promising advances, HPE's stock fell 18% over the past week.
